Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《指定幸存者》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on "Designated Survivor"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我的女儿能够看到一位女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would like my daughter to see a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了美利坚合众国的副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}become vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道德委员会刚刚宣布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The House Ethics Committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要展开对议长的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they are opening an investigation into the Speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个伟大的总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dad was a great president.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰勒  对你的丧亲之痛我非常遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tyler, I am sorry for your incredible loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛萨诺还活着  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lozano is alive, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局击毙的人是个替身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man the FBI killed was a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰伊·惠特克  国土安全部顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jay Whitaker, Homeland Security Adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛萨诺是个很厉害的士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lozano was a total soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴我们抓到了这个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just glad we caught the son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经知道白宫里有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've known that someone in the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让柯克曼成为指定幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}made Kirkman designated survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人可能还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This person may still be active.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森  我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Jason. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}帕特里克·劳埃德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里克·劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Patrick Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clockwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们重回正轨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴我们能有机会深入研究这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad we had a chance to dig in on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能够在不影响安全的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we can expedite TSA screenings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加快安检速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without sacrificing security,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这钱就花得值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's money well-spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统就希望能提高人民的生活质量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the president is all about making people's lives easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们或许可以在北约峰会之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we can put this on his radar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向他提出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}after the NATO summit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期间你会给我需要的数据吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, you'll get me that data?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-成交  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Consider it done. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}包裹已发出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}包裹已发出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚来白宫的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, here's something I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I came to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治·华盛顿在独立战争期间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George Washington ran America's first spy ring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组建了美国第一个间谍网\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}during the Revolutionary War.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的特工们传递了英国军队的动向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His agents relayed British troop movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时连电话都还没有呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they didn't even have cellphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看起来不太高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He doesn't look very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也戴着木质假牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you probably wouldn't want to smile either
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就不会想笑了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you had wooden teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-总统先生  -总统来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. President! - It's the President!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说今天有一群特殊的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard that we had some very special guests
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}here in the White House today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括里士满总统的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Including President Richmond's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰勒  很高兴再次见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tyler, really good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same here, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请容我介绍来自新奥尔良的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Allow me to introduce the student orchestra of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特·里士满高中的学生管弦乐队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert Richmond High School in New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸见到大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is an honor to meet all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到传闻说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I heard a rumor that we're gonna get to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午能听到你们的表演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you perform later this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也听到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard that rumor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经等不及了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't wait to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有任何需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if there's anything you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要犹豫直说就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}please don't hesitate to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟您合张影吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I take a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be my pleasure. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的支持  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for doing this, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李奥和佩妮去了总统行宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With Leo and Penny up in Camp David,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫里又能迎来些孩子挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, it's nice to have young people in the White House again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你与这些学生分享\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's great to see you sharing your passion for music
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对音乐的热情真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with these students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, I can't take credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个团队其实是一个全国性项目的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This group is actually part of a national program
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个项目资助公立学校的艺术教育\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that funds the arts in public schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那挺不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但遗憾的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个项目要终止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it, um, might all come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会批准提供资金的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, when the funding was approved,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设定了"日落条款"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congress put in a sunset clause,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}对计划规定失效日期\N到期后除非再次得到批准  否则就此失效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此拨款每五年要更新一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so the grant has to be renewed every five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么时候到期  -下个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When's it expire? - Next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这可能就结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, this might be the end of playing music
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多孩子的音乐路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for a lot of these kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很多人家里支付不起私人课程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, you know, most of their families can't afford private lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家当时也付不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mine couldn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当年在小学乐团里吹小号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I played trumpet in my elementary school band.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道您参与过演奏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I didn't know you played.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没法说那叫演奏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I wouldn't exactly call it playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  我吹得特别烂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, it was pretty awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但重要的是那段经历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it was the experience that mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常赞同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That -- I-I -- couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音乐构成了我的全部生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Music shaped my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李奥也对音乐很痴迷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leo's all about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我得承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能无法体会到电子音乐的魅力所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think I can get into dubstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不一定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸向我介绍了勃拉姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dad introduced me to Brahms,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}德国古典音乐作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我让他迷上了电台司令[摇滚乐队]\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got him hooked on Radiohead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证  我会跟进拨款的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise you. I will look into the grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这种小事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know this is small stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您手上的事情比太微不足道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}compared to everything else you've got going on --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  这不是小事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, it's not small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的所有学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think every student in this country
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都应该有机会接受艺术方面的熏陶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should have access to the arts for their education.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸能帮上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be an honor to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那我们演奏会见  -我都等不及了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll see you at the concert? - I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查了她所有的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went through all of her files.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分都和布朗宁·里德有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of them have to do with Browning Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她出外勤了  所以要关闭无线电联络\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe she's out in the field and had to go radio silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道威尔士不怎么按常理出牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know Wells isn't exactly by-the-book, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她要是在查什么  肯定会告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, if she working something, she would've let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那杰森·亚特伍德呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Jason Atwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是带杰森一起去的北达科他州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, she did bring him to North Dakota with her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许  也许他们俩联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe -- maybe he's talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经问了  他什么都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already tried. He doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且  汉娜告诉过我她不想让他插手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, Hannah told me she sidelined him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她住哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's she staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是她的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去她房间里看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's check her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特勤局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我们开门吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you open this door, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任何发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查下安保监控录像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's check the security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看路啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, eyes on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  霍斯拉滕的道德委员听证会要开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Hookstraten's Ethics Committee hearing's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我知道媒体在今天的简报里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, at least I know what the press is gonna ask me about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会问我什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in today's briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都爱听道德丑闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody loves an ethics scandal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是关于副总统的流言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially given the V.P. rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓副总统的流言都只是流言而已  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The V.P. rumors are just that, Seth. Rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情总能有巧妙的方法变为现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things have a tricky way of becoming reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着看听证会怎么样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just see how this hearing goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没评价我的新发型呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey! You didn't say anything about my haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没注意到呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来都一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it looks the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往的好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It always looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  剪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is -- what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这次出差剪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it for the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没意识到参加北约峰会能让你如此激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow, I didn't realize you were so excited for a NATO summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是为了北约峰会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, not for NATO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在空军一号[总统专机]里拍很多照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I figure I'll be taking a lot of pictures on Air Force One.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前坐过飞机的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, you've been on a -- a plane before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没有坐过空军一号啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ooh, not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}众议院道德委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我的同事在此将判定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What my colleagues and I are here to determine is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的土耳其之行与随后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether or not there was any quid pro quo involved
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你参与起草土耳其军事援助法案间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}between your trip to Turkey and your subsequent co-sponsorship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否存在任何的利益交换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the military aid bill to that country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你的直言  议员女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate your candor, Congresswoman,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就能直接否认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I can categorically deny
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这二者之间有任何的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that there was any connection between the two events.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土耳其之行的目的是在于农业方面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trip was about agricultural methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此次行程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did anyone from the Turkish military or government
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任何来自土耳其军方或政府的人与你联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}contact you during your time in Turkey
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就军事援助事宜以任何方式进行过讨论吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to discuss military aid of any nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  他们没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, they did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  这只是个巧合吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, it's just a coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有跟你一起出差的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that everyone who went on that trip with you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后都投票赞成军事援助计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}later voted in favor of the military aid package?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙杜尔议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman Saldua,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他279位国会议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}279 other members of Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也支持了那项法案  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}also supported that bill, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过你的问题来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, by your question,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不仅对我的忠诚表示了怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you are not only impugning my integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还责难了我那些再也不能到场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but also that of my colleagues
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为自己辩护的同事们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who are no longer here to defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并非我的目的  议长女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't my intent, Madame Speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请听我一言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I may?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你们都是国会新成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of you are new to Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一点我们是一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but one thing we have in common
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都曾宣誓要维护宪法权威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the oath we took to uphold the Constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来我竭尽全力践行自己的誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've always done my best to live up to that oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许可供你们查证的真凭实据并不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There may be little hard evidence here for you to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我这一生为公众所尽的义务真切地摆在眼前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but there is a lifetime of public service to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是问题的关键所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's what's at stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我最想为自己做的辩护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's also my best defense --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的功绩和我的名誉之名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my record and my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了投票表决的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When it comes time to vote...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们能就此进行投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you will vote on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只有一个有用的摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course they only have one working camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于威尔士探员的  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about Agent Wells, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被绑架了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚在她住处的停车场内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last night, in the parking lot of her motel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辆货车停下来  那些人把她绑走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a van pulled up and they grabbed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是谁干的  -我们不知道  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who? - We don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们追踪了那辆车  但车牌是偷来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We traced the vehicle, but the plates came back stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我希望各部门彻查此事  -已经吩咐下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I want every agency on this. - It's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前她在调查什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was she closing in on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在查布朗宁·里德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was looking into Browning Reed --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的一个军事承包商\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a former military contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员认为其前任执行董事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells is convinced that the ex-C.E.O. Patrick Lloyd's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里克·劳埃德涉嫌参与这起阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}involved with the conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她掌握了什么证据吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she have any evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今为止  这还只是猜想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right now, it's just a working theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无法证明他与爆炸案有直接关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have anything directly tying him to the bombing, yet --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚未找到任何确凿的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no smoking gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们已对他进行全天候监视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we've got eyes on him 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳埃德住在弗吉尼亚州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lloyd lives in Virginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近他一直穿梭于各地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but lately he's been traveling the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树立他的政治形象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}building up his political profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午他要向在市中心集会的极右派发表演说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This afternoon, he's speaking to an alt-right gathering downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用一切可以利用的资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use every resource available to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找到威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but find Agent Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人买这玩意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people still buy this stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我说什么好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶时髦的人都喜欢模拟信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hipsters love analog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弄到了定向麦克风和接收器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a shotgun mic and receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收音范围达914米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Range of 1,000 yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪器在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The nano tracker inside --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重量完全可以忽略不计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}negligible weight difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪半径为16公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tracking radius of 10 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局没玩意可玩了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bureau run out of toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么快就能给我搞到这些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for the quick turnaround.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠你个人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  有件事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, I have something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为您一定想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you're going to want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于北约峰会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about the NATO summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗耳恭听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚跟新任法国大使见过面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just came from meeting the new French ambassador,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要谈的第一件事就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the first thing he wanted to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was nukes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核弹怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国自由党几十年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Liberals in France have been railing against
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在反对核扩散\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nuclear escalation for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在  甚至是保守党的人都开始好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now, even the conservatives are beginning to wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为什么要花那么多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why they're spending so much damn money
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来维持部署在欧洲的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just to maintain weapons in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布范大使四处暗示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ambassador Bouvar broadly hinted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们愿意逐步削减军备  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that it's an opening to de-escalate, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是我没搞错的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but unless I'm missing something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们削减军备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if we reduce our arsenal,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么能保证我们的敌人不趁机作势呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what stops our adversaries from taking advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果西方国家能向俄罗斯展示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the West could show Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的确在认真考虑此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we were serious about laying down our weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么他们就可能会觉得削减军备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they might see that it's safe for them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于他们自身也是安全的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to start laying down theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们不这么认为呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if they don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就要一步步来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we'd do it incrementally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法互惠互利  我们就停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if there's no reciprocity, we stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是个机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, it's a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在任的时候可没有这种机会  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a chance I never got, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅要法国和美国同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would take more than France and the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-所有盟国都要同意  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The entire alliance would have to be on-board. - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细节都写在里面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The details are all in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时  我需要你同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, I will need permission
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我跟法国及另外几个北约成员国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to open any backdoor communication with the French
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行秘密交谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a few of our other NATO partners,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要立即行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we'll have to act fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的这个时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This time tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就要去多伦多参加峰会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everyone'll be heading to Toronto for the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特伦顿警局十五分钟前打电话说找到了那辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trenton P.D. called in the plate 15 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-空的  -是的  什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Empty? - Yeah, top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不会给我们留下什么线索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not like they're gonna leave us any breadcrumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她不在里面也是好事  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, it's better than her being in there. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可如果他们抓走她不是为了杀她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, if they didn't take her to kill her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他们抓她是为了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, what do they want with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛萨诺在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Lozano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他说我要跟他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You tell him I want to talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可问题不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The problem, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民众对这件事的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}isn't public support for the issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是采矿和公用事业公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's the mining and utility companies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在互相争斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that put up the biggest fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就不该拿干净的水源来做所谓斗争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clean water shouldn't even be a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说的这些公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These companies that you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要为未来考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}need to start working for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道这些企业高管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know that business execs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会考虑最低成本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}only think about bottom-line costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们只关心成本的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if their only concern is costs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你应该提醒他们处理这个烂摊子要花多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you should remind them how much it costs to clean up their mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其在我们向他们征收罚款后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially after we start fining them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  布莱恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔  请随我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听证会怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, how did the hearing go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说  我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Honestly, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我表现得还行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I represented myself well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦也这么觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron thought I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那种地方很难摸透\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's a hard room to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定做得很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you knocked it out of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总统先生  就算道德委员会没有发现什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, sir, even if the Ethics Committee finds no wrongdoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指控依然存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the accusation will always be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我会支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said I would stand behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我是认真的  -谢谢  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I meant it. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要继续工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I intend to keep doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公务可不会停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The business of governing doesn't stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有道德调查也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even for an ethics inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天早上见到了里士满总统的儿子泰勒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I met with President Richmond's son Tyler this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟来自新奥尔良一所高中的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was with a group of music students
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些学音乐的学生一起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from a high school in New Orleans
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这所高中是以他父亲的名字命名的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that had just been named after his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟我说他们学校的音乐项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, he told me that their music program
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要没有资金了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was gonna lose their funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对联邦艺术资助金法案熟不熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How familiar are you with the federal art grants
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能帮忙推动此类项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that make these kind of programs possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得这个法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember that bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我的某些更保守的同事能通过这个法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sunset clause was added to get it past
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中还加入了"日落条款"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some of my more conservative colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会重新授权拨款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How fast do you think we can get Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to reauthorize the grant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望我能帮上你和泰勒  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I could help you and Tyler with this, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但必须得经过筹款委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it has to go through the Ways and Means Committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而委员会的主席是欧文·沙杜尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is chaired by Owen Saldua,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正好是道德委员会中负责调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who just happens to be leading the charge against me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对我的指控的人  -你开玩笑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- in the Ethics Committee. - You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  并不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我无法对他施加影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have any leverage with him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你或许有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you might.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙杜尔是无党派人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saldua's an Independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能会听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He might just listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我会联系他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I'll reach out to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼夫人  谢谢你今天带我们参观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks again, Mrs. Kirkman, for showing us around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气  叫我艾丽克斯就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, please, call me Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很棒  也让我很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was great, and it made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他们做的事情都充满了热情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're so passionate about what they're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还很崇拜你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they adore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们能让我跟着  我已经很幸运了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm just lucky they let me hang around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么谦虚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't sell yourself short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出来你跟他们关系很融洽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could tell you have a way with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说也受益匪浅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's -- it's been good for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们都挺不错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kids are good... really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住进总统行宫算是个改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Camp David's been a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩妮倒还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not so much for Penny
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她视所有事情都为一种挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because, you know, she sees everything as an adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是李奥  我觉得他认为我们在惩罚他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Leo, I-I think he thinks we're punishing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I know how hard it can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道有多么难受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, being a part of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这甚至都不是你所要求的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you didn't even sign up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, neither did you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你似乎应对得非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you seemed to cope really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这对谁来说都不是易事  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I guess it's -- it's not easy for anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前希望我的孩子们可以拥有非凡的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used to want my kids to have extraordinary lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我只想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now I-I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想他们简单平凡就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want some semblance of ordinary, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我的经验来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From, um, my experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们会触底反弹的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}kids can bounce back from a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是你们要团结在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What matters is, is that you stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我们会带领美国重振雄风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请  劳埃德先生  借过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right this way, Mr. Lloyd. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走过金属探测门之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Place all metal objects in the tray
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请把所有金属物品放入盒内  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- before stepping through the metal detector. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  您的胸针\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, your lapel pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你在开玩笑对吗  -机器非常敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're kidding, right? - It's a very sensitive machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好吧  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菜一碟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy like Sunday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你点小费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a little tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你留着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, you can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙杜尔议员来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman Saldua's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议员  欢迎来到白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman, welcome to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请坐  -谢谢您  这是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please. - Thank you, sir. It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前一直希望我可以尽早拿到邀请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hoping I might get an invitation soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是考虑到目前的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}though I am a bit wary about coming in today,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于今天是否来拜访我还是心存顾虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}given the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并非要干预正在进行的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not here to meddle in any ongoing investigations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也十分抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I am very sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直没有机会见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we haven't had the chance to meet yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在摸索我的从政之路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm still trying to find my way around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as I'm sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天如此  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every day, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我相信我们可以大展拳脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm convinced we can do some great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴能听你这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多工作要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我在思考教育的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today, I was thinking about education.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见了新奥尔良州的一些高中生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I met some high school students from New Orleans --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部分音乐项目是由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}part of a music program funded by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国艺术基金会资助的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the National Endowment for the Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不幸的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的资金快要用完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their funding's about to run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艺术教育是我们筹措到下一笔预算之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arts education is certainly something to look at
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须去关注的板块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as we approach the next budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子等不了那么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These kids can't wait that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的拨款下个月到期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their grant expires next month
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非国会可以再次通过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless Congress re-approves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想也许我们可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I was hoping that maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一个特事特办的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we could find a way to fast-track it --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它附加到其他项目中去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tack it on to something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我无礼  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Respectfully, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在国会的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ran for Congress
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是要阻断这种暗箱操作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to avoid that kind of back-room dealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我无礼  这不是什么暗箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Respectfully, this isn't a back room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是白宫总统办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the Oval Office of the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种幕后操手正是华盛顿几十年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These kind of riders have been part of the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直存在的一类问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in Washington for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮帮我  我帮帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, you scratch my back, I scratch yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议员先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个项目影响的不仅是新奥尔良的高中学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this won't just affect high school students in New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是全国性项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a national program.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-后果将会  -我和大家一样热爱音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The ramifications... - Look, I love music as much as anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但许多民众认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But a lot of folks think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该把所有精力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we should throw everything we've got
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花在发展科技  工程  数学等学科上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into science, technology, engineering, math.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以往美国在这些领域首屈一指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We used to lead the world in those areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在我们只能算是中等水平了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, we're barely in the middle of the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think our children
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不该被迫在艺术与科学之间做选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should be forced to choose between art or science.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  如果我们能筹措出这笔预算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm happy to debate this, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很乐意支持这个立场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when we put together the next budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年是清算之年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the year of our reckoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上的其他国家就快要追赶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rest of the world is catching up to what we've known --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们长久以来的成就了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that for far too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府想要绑架我们的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}government has tried to hijack our identities,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制我们的生活  给我们的孩子洗脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}control our lives, and brainwash our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以后再也不会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But no longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们正在崛起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No longer because we are rising up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没错  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah! -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次运动是我们国家的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This movement is the future of our nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有非法的政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and no -- no illegitimate government,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有非法的总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no illegitimate president,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能阻挡我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is going to stand in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是法索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Foerstel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳埃德怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在总结他的啤酒馆暴动宣言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just wrapping up his Beer Hall Putsch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是鼓舞人心  随时向我汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inspiring. Keep me posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}雷伯恩众议院办公楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  哥哥  这是我第一周上班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, man. It's my first week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就来找我套消息了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're already shaking me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然兄妹是用来干嘛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what else are cousins for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是让你泄露\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, I'm not asking for any state secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家秘密之类的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to know what your take
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上听证会情况有多糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was on how things went down this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道吉田议员很是感动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know Congresswoman Yoshida was impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有德拉克罗瓦和哈蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Delacroix and Harmon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  只有这几个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿到的支持只有这么点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We didn't get more support than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  还有一些听证成员没联系完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, they still have more witnesses to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你认为票数是九比三  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you think it's gonna be a 9-3 against.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  我可能有错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么风声我会告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll call you if I hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  表哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九比三吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}9 to 3 against?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是估计而已  议长女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an estimate, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还有别的证人要传唤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They still have other witnesses to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  官僚主义者总是只简单确认已知事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, bureaucrats who simply confirm the facts they already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出了趟差以及法案被通过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took a trip and there was a bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人还是可能改变主意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the others can still change their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为自己做得比这更好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I did better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很好  议长女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you did fine, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个非正规法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a kangaroo court.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会免除我的议长职务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're going to strip me of my Speakership.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭他们之力无法罢免你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they can't do that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只能向众议院提出建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can only recommend to the full House.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还可以抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can still fight this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用什么来抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实无法改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The facts won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天与委员会的会面  我已尽了全力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave it my best shot in there today with the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你觉得面对众议院之时  情况能更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What makes you think I'll do any better in the House?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样我们就有时间组织公关活动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it'll give us time to organize a campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你的资料向全国媒体公布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll put your profile out there in the national media,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们尽量拖延这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll drag it out as long as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到公众舆论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until public opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转向你这一方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}swings the vote in your direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能给我出了个主意  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may have just given me an idea, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一搏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A last hurrah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天能过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢  很高兴认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Thank you. It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标正在离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Target on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到  准备移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On it. Ready to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}距离\N238米
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将各项信息浓缩成几个要点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll boil the message down to a handful of talking points,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后于峰会前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}get those out to some key media outlets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通报各大重要媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in anticipation of the summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您之后在多伦多的讲话将建立于此基础上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then your speech in Toronto will build on those.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少点国家主义  增加多邦合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Less nationalism, more multinationalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是要点所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在减少全球范围内的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And let's be specific
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军事热区问题上  我们要明确点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about reducing military hot spots around the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-建立意识  -好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Build awareness. - Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我准备好草稿以便您在飞机上看  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll have a draft for you to read on the plane. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就艺术教育拨款问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I, uh -- I've reached out to Leg Affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系了立法事务局的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about that arts education grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有进展吗  -他们正在努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Any luck? - They're trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看起来沙杜尔议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it seems Congressman Saldua
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在众议院里的财权掌控得比较严\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}controls the purse strings in the House pretty tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数代表都没有投票经历  很难说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of these new reps don't have any voting history to speak of,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们要自己摸索了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we're feeling our way in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要了一份名单  名单上每个选举区  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I did request a list of every Congressional district
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-至少有一所学校参与该项目  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- with at least one school in the program. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也许能让他们再仔细考虑一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That might make them think twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们知道如果停止拨款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}knowing they're gonna have to face their constituents
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.59,0:24:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就要面对自己的选民了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if they let the grant expire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -先别说谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Don't thank me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.07,0:24:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在努力呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm still working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.53,0:25:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在听证会上说什么并不重要  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It really didn't matter what I said in that hearing, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我不能讨论仍在进行中的道德调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know I can't discuss an ongoing ethics investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.21,0:25:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其对方是当事人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially not with its subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你想踢我出局  欧文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also know you want me out, Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.22,0:25:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你所代表的政治活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe the kind of politicking you represent
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.54,0:25:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经成为过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should be a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.85,0:25:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白这对于传递消息有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand that's good for messaging,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.31,0:25:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是关于我们老派政客有一点你不了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but what you don't realize about us old-school politicians
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.02,0:25:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明白这些程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that we understand procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.00,0:25:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这些上交到众议院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this goes to the House,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.68,0:25:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少接下来六个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could eat up the next six months at least
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.59,0:25:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会被听证会  动议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with hearings and motions
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.61,0:25:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和传讯所吞噬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and subpoenas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.05,0:25:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这是威胁吗  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that a threat? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.62,0:25:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实恰恰相反\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite the opposite, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.81,0:25:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意给你让路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm willing to get out of your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.79,0:25:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.53,0:25:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想为国家着想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want what's best for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.98,0:25:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我会退位让贤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I'll step aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.14,0:25:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辞去议长职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}resign the Speakership,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.25,0:25:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.26,0:25:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.43,0:25:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.53,0:25:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想你做一件事  欧文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I want something from you, Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.71,0:26:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我走之前  我希望公众艺术教育\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want the public arts education funding reauthorized
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.57,0:26:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次获得批准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.56,0:26:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这项行动仍然有可行性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The operation is still viable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.36,0:26:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我会清除你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right now, I'm brooming any connection
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.85,0:26:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布朗宁·里德以及国会任务之间的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}between you, Browning Reed, and the Capitol mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.54,0:26:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then, I want to know why
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.32,0:26:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么两名联调局调查员来调查我的物业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}two federal investigators were on my property.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.70,0:26:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你别担心  我会去查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about it. I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.50,0:26:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}000034音频
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.32,0:26:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快  就不会再有书面记录等等的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, there'll be no paper trail whatsoever,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且威尔士探员已被抓获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Agent Wells is contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.01,0:26:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.64,0:26:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那媒体方面呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what about the, uh -- the press angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.66,0:26:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃布·莱纳德的一切都步入了正轨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything's on track with Abe Leonard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.47,0:26:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给他的一切  他都消化了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's eaten up everything I've fed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.58,0:26:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他以为自己会成为揭发水门事件的记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He thinks he's another Woodward and Bernstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.93,0:26:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们什么时候能看到他采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, when are we going to see something from him, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.03,0:26:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any day, I expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.95,0:26:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定联调局不会发现任何端倪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're sure that the FBI has no idea what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.50,0:26:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的调查局现在都专注于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the agencies are focused on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.11,0:26:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁克硬盘上的三个目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the three targets from Brooke's hard drive --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.94,0:26:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金门大桥  胡佛水坝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Golden Gate Bridge, the Hoover Dam,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.46,0:26:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及自由女神像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the Statue of Liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.34,0:26:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-控制权在我们手里  -那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have operational control. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.54,0:26:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jay...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.99,0:26:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就快接近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.67,0:26:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许没有总统地位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We might not have the Presidency,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:27:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以十分肯定  不久以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you can be damn sure that, before long,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.25,0:27:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能掌控整个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will have the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.76,0:28:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经调查过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done a multi-agency document search
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何含有白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for any files with the words
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.82,0:28:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及布朗宁·里德字眼的多家机构文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"White House" and "Browning Reed" in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.41,0:28:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我设法找到的只有这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I've managed to find was this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.10,0:28:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有五个文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's, like, five files.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.49,0:28:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这怎么可能  -可能是有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How's that possible? - Someone would've had to physically
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.76,0:28:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西翼手动清理了这些文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}remove these documents from the West Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.08,0:28:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定会有数字记录的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's got to be a digital record.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.79,0:28:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在搜索数据库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still poring through the database.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎自从国会袭击案之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it seems since the attack at the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.93,0:28:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提及到布朗宁·里德的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}references to Browning Reed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.19,0:28:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被系统删除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have been systematically deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.06,0:28:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想掩盖他们的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone's covering their tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.09,0:28:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们找到删除文件的人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we find out who deleted these files...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就找到了叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We find our traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.25,0:28:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟泰勒·里士满聊了很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a long talk with Tyler Richmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.61,0:28:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有个让人心疼的地方  你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was just this sadness about him, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.45,0:28:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一点都不了解他父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't get to know his dad growing up --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.56,0:28:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部的政治观点还有白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all the politics and then the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.47,0:29:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他仍在追赶他的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I felt like he's still chasing his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想我们的孩子变成这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I so don't want that for our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.46,0:29:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.85,0:29:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们是在保护他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know we're trying to protect them,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.34,0:29:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们跟我们一起不是更好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but aren't they better off with us --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.78,0:29:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们两个一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.67,0:29:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不是时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.79,0:29:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我很抱歉  但\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm -- I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.55,0:29:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.66,0:29:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.30,0:29:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.47,0:29:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  霍斯拉滕议长来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, Speaker Hookstraten?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.16,0:29:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.19,0:29:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先工作吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you get back to your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.79,0:29:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽克斯...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.45,0:29:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  我们迟点再聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.58,0:29:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔  来  请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble, please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.76,0:29:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟委员会那边聊过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you speak with the committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.78,0:29:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私底下聊过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unofficially.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.11,0:29:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尽快跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I wanted to speak to you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.01,0:29:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.98,0:29:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了要辞职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've decided to resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.65,0:29:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长职位吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Speakership?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.43,0:29:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我的席位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.96,0:29:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.48,0:29:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔  这样做没有任何意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble, that doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.24,0:30:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道德委员会准备要投票反对我  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Ethics Committee is going to vote against me, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.40,0:30:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要向白宫建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}recommend to the House
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.81,0:30:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开除我议长的职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I be removed as Speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.76,0:30:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在白宫还有盟友呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have friends in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.19,0:30:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不够的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.70,0:30:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For better or worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.65,0:30:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于新国会来说我代表着旧的那一套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I represent old politics to a new Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.48,0:30:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是新的政治吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is the new politics?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.74,0:30:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是扫清障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我会战斗到最后一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said I would fight till the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.05,0:30:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得现在是时候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I can see now that this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.73,0:30:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当初来华盛顿是为了服务国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I came to Washington to serve,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.04,0:30:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却不能像我保证的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I can't represent my constituents
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.20,0:30:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代表我的选民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the way they deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.43,0:30:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔  求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.71,0:30:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我能做些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.69,0:30:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都做不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.97,0:30:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's out of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.45,0:30:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我至少还有个小小的好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, I do have a little bit of good news, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.10,0:30:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我作为议长所做的最后贡献\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As my last act as Speaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议会会继续资助艺术教育经费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the House will refinance the arts education funding
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.90,0:30:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给罗伯特·里士满高中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for Robert Richmond High
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及依靠这笔经费的公立学校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and all the other public schools that depend on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.38,0:30:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.42,0:30:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙杜尔说他绝不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saldua said he'd never do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.50,0:30:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个犯人都有最后一餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, every inmate gets a last meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.56,0:30:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是要求了一点肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked for a little bit of pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.20,0:31:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  你是我在华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you're the best ally
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.03,0:31:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到的最好的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could've ever hoped for in Washington, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.53,0:31:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸和你共事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been an honor serving with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.59,0:31:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.33,0:31:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.04,0:31:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.80,0:31:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很欣赏你的姿态  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate the gesture, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.91,0:31:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们不能寄希望于国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we can't take on Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.32,0:31:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在考虑寄希望于其他的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm thinking of taking on something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.58,0:31:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行妈妈  只有总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Mom, only the president gets to wave
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.46,0:31:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在登上空军一号的时候可以挥手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when he steps on Air Force One.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.68,0:31:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不能嘚瑟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't get a shout-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.61,0:31:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又不是超级碗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not the Super Bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.39,0:31:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- hey, uh, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.47,0:31:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带厚衣服的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I'm bringing warm clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.49,0:31:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我爱你  再见  -我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, I love you too, bye.  - Oh, love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.03,0:31:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谁啊  -北约会议演练而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who's that? - Uh, just some NATO prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.25,0:31:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道空军一号上的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, did you know that they charge you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.24,0:31:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要收钱的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the food on Air Force One
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.58,0:31:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃不吃都要收钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether you actually eat it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.23,0:31:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你知不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, did you know
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱怨空军一号上的食物这种行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that complaining about the meals on Air Force One
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.22,0:31:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟告诉别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the same thing as telling people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.49,0:31:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看不上波士顿的学校一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you went to school outside of Boston?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.49,0:31:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}哈佛大学  麻省理工等五所名校皆位于波士顿
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.27,0:31:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-剑桥就不在波士顿  -老天  \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cambridge is outside of Boston. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.71,0:31:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确定你很快就有机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm sure you'll ride on the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.28,0:31:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐那个飞机了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}soon enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.92,0:31:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总得有人镇守大局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody's got to stay here to hold down the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.66,0:31:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  希望你喜欢飞机上的脆饼干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, I hope you enjoy your in-flight pretzels
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.43,0:31:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为到时候我就是整个白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I will be the highest ranking person
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.09,0:32:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职务最高的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.99,0:32:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.54,0:32:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你已经找到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me that you found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是时间问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only a matter of time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.48,0:32:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会找到她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.49,0:32:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有了新发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, there is a new development.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.13,0:32:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到方法锁定叛徒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think there's a way to identify the traitor
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.79,0:32:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过追踪电脑痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}through a computer trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.19,0:32:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很艰难  但是会有结果的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna be pain-staking, but it will get results.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.87,0:32:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the meantime, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.79,0:32:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得谈谈你明天的行程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we need to discuss your trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.35,0:32:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为你现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think it's a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.23,0:32:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开白宫是个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for you to leave the White House right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.47,0:32:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克  我理解你的担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike, I understand your concerns,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我必须得去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.82,0:32:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会退缩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.84,0:32:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我坚持还要加倍安保\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I insist we increase your security even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.75,0:32:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为有必要就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do whatever you think is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.44,0:32:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我们就快找出叛徒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, if we're this close to finding the traitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.02,0:32:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你留在华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you here in Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-先生  我  -总统说得很对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir, I--  - Wait, no, the president's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.65,0:32:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人手太过于分散\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're spread way too thin as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.05,0:32:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有四个人了解全部情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's only four of us who know the full extent of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.78,0:32:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有三个都在这间房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and three of us are in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.47,0:32:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  你的安全仍是我第一要务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, your safety is still my primary directive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.92,0:32:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那由你来亲自挑选我的安保人员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you handpick my detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.37,0:32:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你信任他们的话  我就信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you trust them, I trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.00,0:32:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想让你留在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, I want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.11,0:32:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.72,0:32:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.13,0:33:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我够不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.21,0:33:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.19,0:33:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都以为你要放我鸽子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was starting to wonder if you'd stood me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.34,0:33:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.60,0:33:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.73,0:33:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.99,0:33:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我之前说的话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it about what I said earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.80,0:33:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我保证不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.46,0:34:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是思绪很乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just got a lot on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.46,0:34:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  咱们去做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, let's get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.40,0:34:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  我很担心你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能从你脸色看出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see it in your face --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.90,0:34:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份工作对你产生了负面影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the toll this job is taking on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.19,0:34:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你不能把所有的事情都告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I know you can't tell me everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.24,0:34:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你可以告诉我一些的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you can tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.76,0:34:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我帮不到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I can't help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.56,0:34:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我在这里的意义又是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then what's the point of me even being here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.40,0:34:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我派了人去帮我做一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked someone to do something for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.07,0:34:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件很危险的事...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...something very dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.71,0:34:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会让他们失去生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and it might cost them their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.34,0:34:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当初在高中时参加合唱团时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was in choir in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.89,0:34:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就从未被邀请到白宫表演过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we were never invited to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.79,0:34:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither were we.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.34,0:34:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你还参加过合唱团  -魔术社\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You were in choir? - Magic club.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.64,0:34:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想想  我们就没被邀请表演过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We never got invited anywhere, now that I think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.20,0:35:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定你能行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure you're up for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.48,0:35:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我想出席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I want to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.24,0:35:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-泰勒  你好吗  -总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tyler, how are you? - Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.41,0:35:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.89,0:35:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.13,0:35:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.66,0:35:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这不是学校礼堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't exactly their high school auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.82,0:35:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会  他们一定会表现得很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on. They're gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.59,0:35:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会让他们永生难忘的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're gonna remember this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.22,0:35:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想第一个告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to be the first to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.38,0:35:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会将重新批准拨款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congress is gonna reauthorize the grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.93,0:35:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真的吗  -真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You serious? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.69,0:35:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该感谢金布尔·霍斯拉滕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should thank Kimble Hookstraten.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.58,0:35:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事是她促成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's the one who made it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.09,0:35:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.89,0:35:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不再与沙杜尔议员有关了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not about Congressman Saldua anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.49,0:35:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.49,0:35:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.61,0:35:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.83,0:35:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  不用鼓掌了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢大家的出席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you all for joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.53,0:35:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们今天到场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that you did not come here today
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.27,0:35:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是来听我的声音的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to listen to my voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.90,0:35:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我会尽量简短发言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I will make this as brief as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.36,0:35:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们即将欣赏的演出  将由来自新奥尔良州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The performance that you are about to hear will be given by
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.22,0:36:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近更名为罗伯特·里士满高中的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the student choir and orchestra of the newly renamed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.63,0:36:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生合唱团与交响乐团带来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert Richmond High School of New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.05,0:36:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与他们一同出席的是泰勒·里士满\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with them today is Tyler Richmond --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.37,0:36:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自己就是天赋异禀的音乐家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a talented musician himself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.17,0:36:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不遗余力地提倡艺术教育\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a great advocate for education in the arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.58,0:36:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早些时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Earlier today,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.31,0:36:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰勒提醒了我艺术是社会的命脉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tyler reminded me that art is the lifeblood of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.67,0:36:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在努力为每个在美国的学子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And as we strive to create a truly comprehensive education
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造一个真正综合的教育体系的过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for every student in America,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.76,0:36:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越发明确地意识到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I realize now more than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.68,0:36:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要一个有能力有激情的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we need someone who is capable and passionate
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.16,0:36:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来统领全局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to lead the charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.05,0:36:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此  我认为没有更好的场合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I can't think of a better setting
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.17,0:36:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来宣布我的教育部长人选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to announce my nominee for Secretary of Education than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.03,0:36:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我来骄傲地介绍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, it is with great pride that I introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.10,0:36:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔·霍斯拉滕议长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaker Kimble Hookstraten.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.66,0:36:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.15,0:37:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸与你在国会共事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been an honor to work with you in Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.04,0:37:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸能为了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it will be my honor to fight beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.13,0:37:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的孩子的教育并肩作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the education of our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.67,0:37:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来各界的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Future leaders in every field,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.02,0:37:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份工作是为了孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this job is about our kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.36,0:37:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个下午也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and this afternoon is, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.62,0:37:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我也很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, it is also my honor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.37,0:37:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来自罗伯特·里士满高中的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to welcome the student orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.08,0:37:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生乐团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Robert Richmond High School.
