Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.18,0:37:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\i1}♪Children♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.30,0:37:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\i1}♪Wade in the water, children♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.16,0:37:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\i1}♪Wade, wade, wade♪  ♪Wade in the water♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.02,0:37:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\i1}♪God's gonna trouble the water♪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.61,0:38:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.53,0:38:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.06,0:38:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次乘空军一号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my first time on Air Force One.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.29,0:38:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, here, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.35,0:38:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不必这样做  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you don't have to do that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.13,0:38:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没事  我知道怎么用这些东西  -好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, no, I know how to work these things. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.53,0:38:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a matter of fact, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.71,0:38:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不如拍张好照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you might as well just do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.60,0:38:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on up those stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.05,0:38:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汤姆  拍一张  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here, Tom, take a -- - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.84,0:38:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和赛斯拍张照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...take a picture with Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.13,0:39:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯  上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth, come on up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.34,0:39:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  先生  您不必这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's okay, sir. You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.93,0:39:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不呢  快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not? Go ahead. Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.83,0:39:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is, uh --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.37,0:39:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是发我妈妈的照片  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is just a photo for my mom, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.35,0:39:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  不是为了发上网或者什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not -- not for Instagram or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.59,0:39:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.80,0:39:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.40,0:39:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以招手吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, can I wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.57,0:39:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我妈肯定会喜欢的  -招手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My mom would really like that. - Wave away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.60,0:39:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.49,0:39:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上飞机吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.28,0:39:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.62,0:39:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not food.
